Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:30.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:36.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:44.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:51.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:01:00.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:16.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:22.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于粮食不足 鹦鹉螺号暂时停靠某座岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,碰巧长嘴硬鳞鱼号 也在此停泊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追捕玛莉与桑森而来的 新亚特兰提斯兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在娜蒂亚面前开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而尼莫也毫不留情地 枪杀了那名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:51.68,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#14 恐鱼之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首两点钟方向发现 不明航行物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于逮到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 应该就是长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 能在这种深度航行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了我们就只有它了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它国家的潜水艇 都还跟玩具没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要追上去吗？船长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将舰首朝两点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰第二种战斗配备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰第二种战斗配备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重复一遍 全舰第二种战斗配备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非战斗员退避至第三区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要去杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着说得那么难听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船是要去对付 长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会原谅他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他可是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论有什么理由 我都绝对不会原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那个时候 要是尼莫船长没开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许死的人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与其害人被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我情愿自己死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不该说出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,医生 玛莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说玛莉昏倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 医生 玛莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的情况如何？医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她可能得了灼热病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,灼热病？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,病名叫什么都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马…马上就能治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 有点困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就用那个魔法药 让她三两下药到病除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种病十分特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光靠这艘船上的药品…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那玛莉她不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不能用你的发明品 还是科学力量想点办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这在我的专业领域之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紧要关头却完全派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 怎么了？ 你很难受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有人有办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是尼莫船长 或许会有解决之道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是灼热病与海洋生物的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 要去找尼莫船长是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你…请你救救玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉得了灼热病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,医生说船长你或许会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你 救救玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要医治灼热病 就得到64号礁岩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们目前离长嘴硬鳞鱼号 只有6000的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是我们布网10天 好不容易才掌握到的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只因为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我们最重要的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只因为这样 你们就要对玛莉见死不救吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说的不能放弃 意思是要去毁了那艘船对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那艘船上也有许多人对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们又要去杀人了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀人与救人 到底哪边比较重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你冷静点听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 振作点啊 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说娜蒂亚跟玛莉都病倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大姐头\N大…大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她得了灼热病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在情况如何？医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们两个最多只能撑两天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿不到药剂 我也无能为力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧 由我去说服尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无法认同他的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么小的孩子正在为病所苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是船长 甚至没半个人来探视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道连一句 安慰鼓励的话都说不出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道这艘船上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都这么没血没泪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？娜蒂亚她？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 听说是被玛莉传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 他们两个 顶多只能再撑个两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离长嘴硬麟鱼号还有3000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,2分钟后进入有效射程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀人与救人 到底哪边比较重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各部门攻击准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航道回转180度 朝64号礁岩全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要放过长嘴硬鳞鱼号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了打倒新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了杀死石像鬼 你一直都是不计任何代价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在却为了孩子 决定半途而废？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,13年前的血海深仇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的弟弟以及双亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不快重复命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航道回转180度 朝64号礁岩前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回转开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,固定于航道125 目标64号礁岩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号远离 距离5000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暂时由你负责\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次再逮到长嘴硬鳞鱼号就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这都要靠你的技术了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是 对吧 操舵长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,64号礁岩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 娜蒂亚他们有救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天之内就会抵达 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了\N太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去找艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 现在最好不要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还真是没半点紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的确也觉得船长变了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他竟然会下令回转 老实说真让我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我并不认为 船长的判断有误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是为了完成目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不该牺牲年幼的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然我们跟石像鬼 又有什么不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想为儿孙报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但并不是为了报仇 就能不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉 我相信尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为有他在 我才能够活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长是个怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用得着说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令人讨厌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是个想拐走我们大姐头 爱装模作样的中年老头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该相反才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你以后长大 可不能变成那种中年男人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是要变成像我这样的好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得还是不要的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种中年男人 根本不是什么好货色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是他还杀了人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们正在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是要互相残杀 直到某一方输了为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论是杀人还是被杀 他们都做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战争是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人会因此而死对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人死了对你来说很罕见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我生长的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都有人因为生病 或是与人起争执而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像我的双亲就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人死并不罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在目前这个世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,位置SP22 RP40
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抵达64号礁岩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷停止于洞穴入口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备潜水球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请带我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不是去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来你们是不会听劝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换上在那里的潜水服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备好了就立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压缩管OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,供气槽正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仪表类无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜水球于洞穴入口处待机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作为采集班 与鹦鹉螺号的中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题吧？\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 准备就绪 随时可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 大家都准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看\N你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王说它也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什么时候做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前看过潜水服的时候 我就想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 没想到真的能做出来 我们还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天才\N天才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉与娜蒂亚就快没命了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出发前我先进行几点说明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于在水中的对话方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离5公尺以内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以使用这个头罩上方的 通话器进行对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该要帮大王加装的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了不起的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 距离超过5公尺 声音就会传递不清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种情况就以灯光来传达讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都会使用摩斯码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后一点要请大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,64号礁岩基本上很安全 但并不是百分之百
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己的安全要由自己来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在水中是讨不到救兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 大家都到水密室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员已进入水密室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备就绪 开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解 开始注水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要慌张 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还能呼吸不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注水完毕 水密室满水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好深喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底有多深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快 没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜水球一号机分离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离着陆点预计还有30
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都是些我没看过的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这些几乎全都是 据说在很久以前就灭绝的鱼种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是洋流与地形的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,64号礁岩自几亿年前 就不受外界影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这根本就是『失落的世界』嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我小时候曾在书本上看过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被考古学家发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会高兴到口水直流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这被称为『深海之雪』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主要为微生物的尸骸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死后反而耀眼夺目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这正是生命的神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希望也能让娜蒂亚看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是潜水球一号机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,采集班已进入洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解 请你继续待机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好壮观 是海草林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 你怎么会拿着那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怕会发生什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就借用了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说得倒好听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是喜欢带枪而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,氧气大约还能撑个1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望不会发生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好深喔 这到底有多深？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度恐怕有1000公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要潜到那么深的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我们的目的地 是那个小洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 要怎么过去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害\N好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回程的时候又该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两边肩膀上有栓子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要拉开就会出现浮球 把身体拉上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来这东西是这么用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该要帮大王加装的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题吧？\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 那我们就加紧行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是药草吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那他们两个有救了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真走运\N真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就够了 采集作业完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们回去吧\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想第一个出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大一只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是古生代泥盆纪的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然敢吓我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,体型大归大 但你终究不过是条鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不试试看怎么晓得？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论什么事都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是全身都覆盖了 坚硬骨甲的甲胄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种程度的枪是伤不了它的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样我们根本出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 大家都把灯关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它以为灯光是食物 才来攻击我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会发生什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有些动物具有趋光性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会习惯朝光源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确我们一熄灯 它就马上离开洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可以用这个 反过来利用这项习性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是开关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把它往下扔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水压变化会使遭到压缩的 两边端子连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 灯会因此点亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以引诱那条鱼过去是吧\N可以引诱那条鱼过去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然有些危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这件事 只有你跟大王才办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你愿意去做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我愿意试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 那就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请快点回来吧 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了 氧气只能再撑5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠你了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好难受 氧气快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 就差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将缆绳绑在岩石上 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缆绳虽然稍微长了点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我又切不断 也只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强！\N强！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠这个根本切不断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好坚固的缆绳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才刚回来就被关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是不慢慢减压的话 会得潜水夫病的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这回算是被孩子救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你们 强、大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我才要谢谢你们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要谢就去谢尼莫船长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光靠我根本救不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢尼莫船长？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烧已经退了 他们两个不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还很担心他们会有什么万一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚跟玛莉已经没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞什么 你们吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别计较那么多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你已经可以坐起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 我好多了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这都全靠尼莫船长 拼了命去帮你们采药草
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你得感谢他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 救了那位尼莫船长的 可是强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再提那件事了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是尼莫船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经将航路回至SB60
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度为三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我也相信船长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:54.87,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:24:02.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:08.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:21.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:31.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.55,0:24:40.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.40,0:24:44.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.57,0:24:49.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.30,0:24:58.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.56,0:25:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号终于发现了 长嘴硬鳞鱼号的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是当娜蒂亚的蔚蓝之水 发出警告的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.53,0:25:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.47,0:25:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为遭到长嘴硬鳞鱼号的 新型武器攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.67,0:25:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而受创的鹦鹉螺号前方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.61,0:25:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟出现了意想不到的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『鹦鹉螺号的最大危机』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.05,0:25:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
